Revision history for Net::Async::WebService::lxd

0.05 Tue 20 Sep 2022 03:29:52 PM CEST
        - more robust when lxd server goes away or other connection problems
        - added stress to test suite
        - _http client now passes on headers, etc to dispatched requests
	- added dependencies

